rder":8,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"-","properties":{},"widgets_values":["# OmniVoice TTS\n\n  ## Auto-Download\n\n  **Models auto-download on first run** - no manual setup needed!\n\n  | Model | VRAM | Size |\n  |-------|------|------|\n  | OmniVoice (fp32) | ~8-12GB | ~4GB |\n  | OmniVoice-bf16 | ~4-6GB | ~2GB |\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Manual Download\n\n  | File | Size | Link |\n  |------|------|------|\n  | OmniVoice (Full fp32) | ~4GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/k2-fsa/OmniVoice) |\n  | OmniVoice-bf16 | ~2GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/OmniVoice-bf16) |\n\n\n```\n  📂 ComfyUI/\n  ├── 📂 models/\n  │   ├── 📂 omnivoice/\n  │   │      ├── 📂 OmniVoice/\n  │   │      │      ├── config.json\n  │   │      │      └── model.safetensors\n  │   │      └── 📂 OmniVoice-bf16/\n  │   │             ├── config.json\n  │   │             └── model.safetensors\n  │   └── 📂 audio_encoders/\n  │          ├── 📂 openai_whisper-large-v3-turbo/\n  │          │      ├── config.json\n  │          │      └── model.safetensors\n  │          └── 📂 openai_whisper-medium/\n  │                 ├── config.json\n  │                 └── model.safetensors\n```\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Nodes\n\n  ### OmniVoice Longform TTS\n  Long-form TTS with smart chunking and optional voice cloning. `ref_audio` is optional — leave disconnected for automatic voice.\n\n  ### OmniVoice Voice Clone TTS\n  Clone a voice from reference audio. `ref_audio` is required. No chunking — for long text use Longform TTS.\n\n  ### OmniVoice Voice Design TTS\n  Design synthetic voices from text descriptions. No reference audio needed.\n\n  ### OmniVoice Multi-Speaker TTS\n  Generate dialogue between multiple speakers using `[Speaker_N]:` tags. Dynamic speaker inputs on ComfyUI >= 0.8.1.\n\n  ### OmniVoice Whisper Loader\n  Pre-load Whisper ASR to avoid re-downloading on each run. Connect to any TTS node's `whisper_model` input.\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Generation Parameters\n\n  | Parameter | Default | Range | Description |\n  |-----------|---------|-------|-------------|\n  | steps | 32 | 4-64 | Diffusion steps. 16=faster, 32=balanced, 64=best quality |\n  | guidance_scale | 2.0 | 0-10 | Classifier-free guidance. Higher = more text-aligned |\n  | t_shift | 0.1 | 0-1 | Time-step shift. Smaller = emphasis on earlier steps |\n  | speed | 1.0 | 0.5-2.0 | Speaking speed. >1=faster, <1=slower |\n  | duration | 0.0 | 0-60 | Fixed output duration (seconds). Overrides speed. 0=auto |\n  | position_temperature | 5.0 | 0-20 | Mask-position randomness. 0=greedy, higher=more random |\n  | class_temperature | 0.0 | 0-5 | Token sampling randomness. 0=greedy, higher=more random |\n  | layer_penalty_factor | 5.0 | 0-20 | Penalty on deeper codebook layers |\n  | denoise | True | — | Prepend denoise token for cleaner output |\n  | preprocess_prompt | True | — | Clean reference audio (remove silences, add punctuation) |\n  | postprocess_output | True | — | Remove long silences from generated audio |\n  | keep_model_loaded | True | — | Keep model in memory (offloads to CPU between runs) |\n\n  **Longform TTS only:**\n\n  | Parameter | Default | Range | Description |\n  |-----------|---------|-------|-------------|\n  | words_per_chunk | 100 | 0-500 | Words per chunk. 0=no chunking. Splits at sentence boundaries |\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Whisper ASR models (for auto-transcription)\n\n  | Model | VRAM | Link |\n  |-------|------|------|\n  | whisper-large-v3-turbo | ~1.5GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-large-v3-turbo) |\n  | whisper-large-v3 | ~3GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-large-v3) |\n  | whisper-medium | ~1.5GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-medium) |\n  | whisper-small | ~0.5GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-small) |\n  | whisper-tiny | ~0.4GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-tiny) |\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Non-verbal expression tags:\n\n  `[laughter]` `[sigh]` `[sniff]` `[question-en]` `[question-ah]` `[question-oh]` `[question-ei]` `[question-yi]` `[surprise-ah]` `[surprise-oh]` `[surprise-wa]` `[surprise-yo]` `[dissatisfaction-hnn]` `[confirmation-en]`\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Voice design attributes (comma-separated):\n\n  | Category | Options |\n  |----------|---------|\n  | Gender | `male`, `female` |\n  | Age | `child`, `young`, `middle-aged`, `elderly` |\n  | Pitch | `very low pitch`, `low pitch`, `medium pitch`, `high pitch`, `very high pitch` |\n  | Style | `whisper` |\n  | English Accents | `american accent`, `british accent`, `australian accent`, `canadian accent`, `indian accent`, `irish accent`, `scottish accent`, `south african accent` |\n  | Chinese Dialects | `四川话`, `陕西话`, `广东话`, `东北话`, `山东话`, `河南话`, `上海话`, `闽南话`, `客家话` |\n\n  **Example:** `female, young, high pitch, british accent, whisper`\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Multi-speaker dialogue format:\n\n  [Speaker_1]: Hello, I'm speaker one.\n  [Speaker_2]: And I'm speaker two!\n  [Speaker_1]: Nice to meet you!\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Links\n\n  - Original [OmniVoice](https://huggingface.co/k2-fsa/OmniVoice)\n  - Models [OmniVoice](https://huggingface.co/k2-fsa/OmniVoice) / [OmniVoice-bf16](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/OmniVoice-bf16)\n  - Paper [arXiv:2604.00688](https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.00688)\n  - Issues [Report Bug](https://github.com/saganaki22/ComfyUI-OmniVoice-TTS/issues)"],"color":"#c09430","bgcolor":"rgba(24,24,27,.9)"}],"links":[[32,26,0,2,0,"AUDIO"],[33,5,0,26,0,"AUDIO"],[34,11,0,26,1,"WHISPER_ASR"],[38,13,0,28,0,"AUDIO"],[39,14,0,28,1,"WHISPER_ASR"],[40,28,0,15,0,"AUDIO"],[41,18,0,29,19,"AUDIO"],[42,19,0,29,22,"AUDIO"],[43,29,0,21,0,"AUDIO"],[44,30,0,16,0,"AUDIO"]],"groups":[{"id":1,"title":"Voice Clone","bounding":[709.3010158767515,2687.6756924882047,776.1213955370494,965.7705864543318],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":2,"title":"Longform Clone","bounding":[1508.7914663102342,2683.3562420791877,785.9196063374911,957.911340119646],"color":"#88A","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":3,"title":"Voice Design","bounding":[833.2977721911777,3713.803130816895,516.6398808317314,802.4348441785855],"color":"#8A8","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":4,"title":"Multi-Speaker","bounding":[1513.1250863903886,3708.479656245934,777.5410785503595,849.2245781794468],"color":"#391466","font_size":24,"flags":{}}],"config":{},"extra":{"ds":{"scale":0.513158118230707,"offset":[560.6556012170282,-2152.4913240699707]}},"version":0.4}